descriptionHTML:
The atmo Strafe watchface brings a classic and timeless watch experience straight into your Android Wear watch.
Detail oriented and pixel perfect - it's an atmo.

Black background, for both square and round devices, with custom coloring of the milliseconds pointer. Yes, it has milliseconds!
comments: Looks good, but function-wise, it's bad! The second is having a seizure, it doesn't move with a constant motion!
Not bad Would like to see numbers
